<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Address Change Notification</title>
    <style>
      /* Inline CSS styles for email compatibility */
      .container {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 600px; /* Maximum width of the container */
        margin: auto; /* Center the container */
      }
      .instruction-box {
        border: 2px solid #df7b01; /* Orange border */
        border-radius: 8px; /* Rounded corners */
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9; /* Light gray background */
        margin: 20px 0; /* Space around the box */
      }
      .instruction-box p {
        margin: 0 0 10px; /* Space between paragraphs */
        line-height: 1.6; /* Increase line height for readability */
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        background-color: #df7b01; /* Orange background */
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px; /* Rounded corners */
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center; /* Center text inside button */
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 style="text-align: center">OTP Verification</h1>
      <div class="instruction-box">
        <p>
          Hi <%= name %>, <br />
          <br />

          <p>We received a request to verify your email address. Please use the OTP code below to verify this change:</p>      
           <p style="text-align: center;font-weight: bolder;font-size: 22.5px; letter-spacing: 10px;"><%= otp %></p>
           
        <p>This code is valid for the next 5 minutes. If you did not request this change, please ignore this email.</p>
          <br />
          <br />
          Thank you, <br />
          The BuzzBreach Team
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
